INSERT INTO `document` VALUES ('2', 'tp5开发的auth权限管理系统的教程（一）【微信部落】', '<p>\r\n	最近一直在看tp5的开发手册，光说不练假把式，实践才能出真知，于是就用tp5写了个auth权限的后台管理系统，这绝对是熟悉一个框架最快的方式了。看到有人下载程序后，却跑不起来，下面我简单讲一下如何把程序运行起来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	下载地址：<a class=\"ke-insertfile\" href=\"https://github.com/ningbnii/auth_tp5\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ningbnii/auth_tp5</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	将程序下载到本地后，搭建一个虚拟机，配置个域名，<span style=\"color:#E53333;\">注意：<span style=\"color:#000000;\">将虚拟机的路径指到public下面，然后导入数据库，修改数据库的配置</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> 别忘了去下载tp5的核心类库，tp5核心类库下载地址：<a class=\"ke-insertfile\" href=\"https://github.com/top-think/framework\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/top-think/framework</a></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"> <span style=\"color:#000000;\">项目后台地址：http://域名/admin</span><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> 用户名：admin<br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> 密码：123456<br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>', '/uploads/image/20160705/20160705190810_58454.jpg', '11', '136', '1467648657', '1467716892', '1', '最近一直在看tp5的开发手册，光说不练假把式，实践才能出真知，于是就用tp5写了个auth权限的后台管理系统，这绝对是熟悉一个框架最快的方式了。', 'thinkphp5,教程,auth,后台管理系统');
INSERT INTO `document` VALUES ('3', '用CSS3实现带小三角形的div框', '<p>\r\n	下面用CSS3分别实现向上、下、左、右的三角形\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class=\"brush:css;toolbar:false;\">/*箭头向上*/\r\n.arrow-up {\r\n    width:0; \r\n    height:0; \r\n    border-left:30px solid transparent;\r\n    border-right:30px solid transparent;\r\n    border-bottom:30px solid #fff;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; border-top:0px;\r\n&nbsp;}\r\n    \r\n /*箭头向下*/\r\n.arrow-down {\r\n    width:0; \r\n    height:0; \r\n    border-left:20px solid transparent;\r\n    border-right:20px solid transparent;\r\n    border-top:20px solid #0066cc;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; border-down:0px;\r\n&nbsp;}\r\n    \r\n /*箭头向左*/\r\n.arrow-left {\r\n    width:0; \r\n    height:0; \r\n    border-top:30px solid transparent;\r\n    border-bottom:30px solid transparent; \r\n    border-right:30px solid yellow; \r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; border-left:0px;\r\n}\r\n   \r\n/*箭头向右*/\r\n.arrow-right {\r\n    width:0; \r\n    height:0; \r\n    border-top:50px solid transparent;\r\n    border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\r\n    border-left: 50px solid green;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; border-right:0px;\r\n&nbsp;}</pre>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>', '/uploads/image/20160705/20160705183107_92285.jpg', '7', '9', '1467714683', '1467714733', '1', '用CSS3实现带小三角形的div框', '用CSS3实现带小三角形的div框');
INSERT INTO `document` VALUES ('4', 'html5 canvas俄罗斯方块', '<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/uploads/image/20160705/20160705183417_30138.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/uploads/image/20160705/20160705183504_61456.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>', '/uploads/image/20160705/20160705183258_74986.jpg', '6', '19', '1467714906', '1467714906', '1', 'html5 canvas俄罗斯方块游戏源码', 'html5,canvas,俄罗斯方块');
INSERT INTO `document` VALUES ('5', 'ionic的ion-infinite-scroll在加载的时候会请求两次', '<p>\r\n	ionic的ion-infinite-scroll在加载的时候会请求两次，这好像是ionic的一个bug，没找到解决方案<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint lang-js\">currentPage = 1  \r\n$scope.hasMoreData = true;\r\n  $scope.loadMore = function(){\r\n      currentPage ++;\r\n      Search.lists($scope.keyword, currentPage,function(res){\r\n        if(res.status == 200){\r\n          if(res.data.produce){\r\n            for (var i = 0; i &lt; res.data.produce.length; i++) { $scope.produces.push(res.data.produce[i]); console.log($scope.produces); } }else{ $scope.hasMoreData = false; } } }); $scope.$broadcast(\'scroll.infiniteScrollComplete\'); }</pre>', '', '2', '33', '1467715432', '1467715478', '1', 'ionic的ion-infinite-scroll在加载的时候会请求两次', 'ionic,ion-infinite-scroll,请求两次');
INSERT INTO `document` VALUES ('6', 'ionic,隐藏底部导航栏', '<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">1.在标签ion-tabs中添加：ng-class=”{‘tabs-item-hide’: $root.hideTabs}”</span><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">2.添加angularjs的指令，源码如下：</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:21px;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint lang-js\">//app已经在其他文件中指定，如var app = angular.module(\"starter\",[\"ionic\"])\r\napp.directive(\'hideTabs\', function($rootScope) {\r\n    return {\r\n        restrict: \'A\',\r\n        link: function(scope, element, attributes) {\r\n            scope.$on(\'$ionicView.beforeEnter\', function() {\r\n                scope.$watch(attributes.hideTabs, function(value){\r\n                    $rootScope.hideTabs = value;\r\n                });\r\n            });\r\n\r\n            scope.$on(\'$ionicView.beforeLeave\', function() {\r\n                $rootScope.hideTabs = false;\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    };\r\n});</pre>\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:\'microsoft yahei\';font-size:14px;line-height:26px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">3.在你想要隐藏的界面标签 ion-view添加表达式hide-tabs=”true”,</span>', '', '8', '12', '1467715644', '1467715644', '1', 'ionic 进入二级目录以后隐藏底部导航栏（tabs）', 'ionic 进入二级目录以后隐藏底部导航栏（tabs）');
